  "instructions": [
    "heat oil in a large pan over medium heat. add onion and cook until translucent.",
    "add garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "add curry paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "add coconut milk, sugar, and fish sauce-free alternative. stir well to combine.",
    "bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "add asian-chive-buchu and Thai basil. stir well to combine.",
    "reduce heat to low and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "serve hot over rice or with naan bread."
